title: Highpower Rifle Reloading- David Tubb (2 Video Set)
description:
This is the most comprehensive, in-depth reloading program ever produced. G. David Tubb is one of the most successful highpower rifle shooters live with 15 national championships in highpower rifle and highpower silhouette shooting. In this program he shows you reloading techniques, methods, tips and secrets that he has learned and used over the past 20 years. You'll see what equipment he uses, how he resized the brass, how he selects his components, how he seats the primers, how he seats and crimps the bullet and much more. Absolutely the best how-to-reload program available for precision long range rifle shooting. A must for serious competitors and long range shooting enthusiasts.
(about 360 minutes)
